{"tid":579761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我敢講，醉酒佬衰撚過哂啲蝻蝗！","createTime":"2018-03-04T01:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:36:04.000Z","uid":116257,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15a842aca0f9354c937319e9e26df0652686e3f1","tid":579761,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"有時收工，幾乎每星期五六晚見咩中環蘭桂坊，尖沙咀諾士佛臺，金馬倫道嗰堆，成撚日都有醉酒佬發酒癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬，飲下酒玩樂下係冇問題，但發覺好撚多唔飲得嘅，飲到貓哂然後發酒癲周圍搞事。<br />\n訓係人地間舖頭外面又有，痴痴呆呆咁企係條馬路中間又有，阻撚住哂，仲衰撚過啲蝻蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過一次啊，路過見到啲救護員係到拍醒啲醉酒佬，好心咁問佢有冇事，洗唔洗白車睇醫生，勸佢唔好再訓係條街到，然後就即刻大大聲咁講：「關你撚事咩，我洗咩睇醫生啊？」，好似想話比人聽自己冇飲醉酒咁，睇見啲救護比人撚真係慘。<br />\n<br />\n香港醉酒依條法例又係無撚用，「任何人被發現在公眾地方醉酒，或在根據任何與酒牌有關的條例而領有牌照的處所內醉酒，均可處罰款$50。」，一係就仿傚新加坡禁撚埋酒去。<br />\n<br />\nbtw...次次見親啲醉酒佬攤咗係路邊，我一定笑撚柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鬼唔望你快啲比蝻亞偷哂你啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be01784cd493a1661b3d5fc949862a62515e0f81","tid":579761,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db76557301183dc531e8a5c04a9b27c9db6c0978","tid":579761,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:52:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一撚樣咁衰<br />\n無衰過架 On9</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc62600ab82288ffc4241d27d9abc9264786332","tid":579761,"uid":116257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be01784cd493a1661b3d5fc949862a62515e0f81","tid":579761,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"睇你都係嗰種麻撚閪煩，唔飲得又要飲到貓哂發酒狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b3695ba02e4dcccba319080a9dad7e84ec2e3b","tid":579761,"uid":28372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be01784cd493a1661b3d5fc949862a62515e0f81","tid":579761,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"好威"},{"pid":"d53a6b2ae141ee0e62dd110d342a83d7b35bbb56","tid":579761,"uid":44504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"咁醉酒蝻蝗點計"},{"pid":"4dea7c28367c65ed32b5e5d6b101eed90b6a3e21","tid":579761,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be01784cd493a1661b3d5fc949862a62515e0f81","tid":579761,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"你咁都唔覺得有問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad3141f92a45d96d89c23a9b219aa9bfeee1885","tid":579761,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"下次見咪吐啖口水過佢嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b369c8408e5acd03e4d746181118e7135cabf99f","tid":579761,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"酒精先係真正毒品，應禁嘅唔禁，大麻就反而係違法，痴線"},{"pid":"b54390c73569a72b6711b228a08509ced2adbfa7","tid":579761,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d53a6b2ae141ee0e62dd110d342a83d7b35bbb56","tid":579761,"uid":44504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"咁醉酒蝻蝗點計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"見親訓係度嘅又或者發酒癲嘅，通常都係自己香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝻又有幾可醉到訓係條街到，通常都係幾個圍圍喂咁繼續飲，<br />\n然後等訓係街到嘅嗰啲埋手做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e18ab8a107a56f38f327bf7ce39aa9638c5d960","tid":579761,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b369c8408e5acd03e4d746181118e7135cabf99f","tid":579761,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"酒精先係真正毒品，應禁嘅唔禁，大麻就反而係違法，痴線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"冇錯，酗酒後果都大啦，cls政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3446153b9b8b84a52ca1f5fadd302740cb6757e4","tid":579761,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"任何人醉酒時在 公眾地方鬧事或行為不檢，可處罰款$250或監禁2個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以告呢條,再唔係撩到佢打鳩你再告多條普通襲擊/傷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}